Summary:
When the user searches for actor through search bar and opens related page, the information (biography) about actor cannot be fully read, since window expanding is not available.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Type Matthew McConaughey in search bar on top of the screen.
2. Click on Matthew McConaughey name in the search results list.
3. Click on the biography text next to the actors image to expand it.
Result: Nothing has changed.